== Chapter 1: Getting Started

This chapter will be about getting started with cloud computing.

We will begin by explaining some background on what the cloud is, the types of services that are available in the cloud, and we will try to define exactly what cloud computing is.

At the end of this chapter you should understand why cloud computing is so important, what are the benefits of cloud computing, and how organizations can benefit from the economics of cloud computing.
